       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ARCANE-DICE.
       AUTHOR. ARCANE-MAGE.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DICE-DATA.
           05  WS-SIDES       PIC 9(3) VALUE 100.
           05  WS-SEED        PIC 9(9) VALUE 87654321.
           05  WS-RESULT      PIC 9(3).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "=== COBOL ENTERPRISE PERCENTILE SYSTEM ===".
           COMPUTE WS-RESULT = FUNCTION MOD(WS-SEED, WS-SIDES) + 1.
           DISPLAY "REPORT: AR-ROLL-D100 LOGGED AT VALUE: " WS-RESULT.
           IF WS-RESULT = 100
               DISPLAY "SUCCESS CRITICAL VALUE ATTAINED."
           END-IF.
           STOP RUN.
